<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.2.10">
<l>iṇṭai koṇṭu toṇṭarētta vevvuḷ kiṭantāṉai</l>
<l>vaṇṭu pāṭum paimpuṟavil maṅkaiyar kōṉkaliyaṉ</l>
<l>koṇṭa cīrāl taṇṭamiḻcey mālaiyī raintumvallā</l>
<l>raṇṭa māḷva tāṇaiyaṉṟē lāḷva ramarulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master this garland of two-times-five [songs]</l>
<l rend="indent">composed in pleasant Tamil with fitting elegance,</l>
<l>By Kaliyaṉ, king of those of Maṅkai in green groves where bees sing,</l>
<l>On the one who lies in Evvuḷ where devotees praise [him] bearing garlands,</l>
<l>[Their] ruling the earth is a certainty; if not,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will rule the world of the immortals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
